  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-013">AI features extend BFF in-process. Memo MUST cite ADR-013 (refined 2026-05-20) as canonical justification. CRUD code MUST NOT directly inject AI-internal types (`IOpenAiClient` / `IPlaybookService`); use `Services/Ai/PublicContracts/` facade. Memo MUST note whether the R3 feature complies (it should — text extraction does not require AI-internal types).</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Memo scope STRICTLY the R3 attachment-payload feature (OC-R4-03). MUST include literal phrase: "one-time retroactive close-out; rule applies prospectively from 2026-05-19" (or near-identical per NFR-02). Edits limited to R3 `notes/` and cross-link updates in R3 lessons-learned + R4 spec/CLAUDE.md — do NOT modify `.claude/`, root CLAUDE.md, or `src/`. VERIFY-then-amend if memo already exists with substantive content.</constraint>
  </constraints>

